        "content": "<p>In one of my file I constructed a similar equivalence using a combination of <br>\n<a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/Mathlib/Algebra/Algebra/Subalgebra/Basic.html#Subalgebra.equivOfEq\">Subalgebra.equivOfEq</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/Mathlib/Algebra/Algebra/Subalgebra/Lattice.html#Algebra.botEquiv\">Algebra.botEquiv</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/Mathlib/Algebra/Algebra/Subalgebra/Lattice.html#Subalgebra.topEquiv\">Subalgebra.topEquiv</a><br>\n<a href=\"https://leanprover-community.github.io/mathlib4_docs/Mathlib/LinearAlgebra/Dimension/FreeAndStrongRankCondition.html#Subalgebra.bot_eq_top_of_finrank_eq_one\">Subalgebra.bot_eq_top_of_finrank_eq_one</a></p>",
